notquiteviet
Da Nang, Vietnam
2922
Reviewed December 4, 2023
Best bánh xèo in Đà Nẵng???
My family can’t get enough of bánh xèo. Since we moved to Da Nang, there’s no other cuisine that we’ve eaten more of. Heard from everyone that this is the spot. Took us a few months to try it, but we finally did and were very happy. It’s down at the very end of a tiny alley with a couple of other bánh xèo joints nearby. Bánh xèo was solid, prices were right, service was quick, and dipping sauce was very good. Can we say that it’s definitively the best place in town? Hard to say, we’ve eaten some really delicious bánh xèo here. But Bánh Xèo Bà Dưỡng is definitely up there and we’ll be back often.
IG: @notquiteviet
Date of visit: November 2023
