Reviewed August 4, 2023
Iconic place in Danang
Delicious crispy pancakes (banh xeo) and grilled meat (nem lui). They are the must order dishes when you are there. Remember to wrap them in rice paper with fresh herbs, dip in the sauce and prepare to be blown away. An iconic place of Danang
