Great Bahn Xeo
This was our first time trying Bahn Xeo and it was delicious. We were here as part of a food tour and would never have picked this place ourselves. We also had some grilled beef and Tiger beer which were also very good. Everything was very fresh and the peanut dipping sauce was a great accompaniment. If you can find it try it out.
