Okay, it's a tourist trap, but it deserves all the hype
Okay, it's a tourist trap, but it deserves all the hype. The Bánh Xèo (Rice Pancake) with Nem Lụi (Meat Skewers) are excellent. This is what every traveller should try when visiting Vietnam - it just screams local and the atmosphere here is made to match.
